From b24b0cf81c5435e7b297eb672743f7e4c9930a6a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OpenEmbedded <oe.patch@oe>
Date: Wed, 6 May 2026 14:48:11 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add mychar driver

---
